title: what good comments (usually) do and do not capture
pid: be5c5fc1-0906-4b4f-a4d6-780765cb0b0a
body: |2-
  - context (esp. why something is done)
  - tradeoffs
  - invariants
  - warnings
  - non-obvious reasoning

  But mere membership in one of the above does not guarantee comment-worthiness.
  Always ask, 'Could the reader need this?'
